description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Diabetes and Endocrinology service at Bolton NHS Foundation Trust currently have a vacancy for a Band 7 Diabetes Specialist Nurse.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The role will require the individual to work as an autonomous, advanced practitioner and support with the delivery of an expert service within the specialist area both from an inpatient and outpatient base. Our new team member must be self-motivated, a team player who is forward thinking and is enthusiastic about the nursing profession. The post holder will be predominantly based within the acute setting providing direct care to inpatients and working as part of the wider MDT to reduce a patient’s length of stay and to support a safe discharge. The post holder will also support community patients from the Bolton Diabetes Centre . The role carries educational responsibilities for patients and other health care professionals which will be delivered in one to one sessions and group environments. The post does involve working within a multidisciplinary team with acute and community colleagues.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The position is for 37.5 hours per week (over a 7 day week) and the post holder must possess excellent communication and interpersonal skills and who can demonstrate good leadership qualities to ensure our patients receive care that is safe, responsive, effective, caring and well lead. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;As a member of our team you will be supported and encouraged to be a part of our on-going service development and dedication to making a difference to patients with diabetes. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameRebecca BradleyJob titleMatron Diabetes and EndocrinolgyEmail addressrebecca.bradley@boltonft.nhs.ukTelephone number01204 463879Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a perspective applicant you are encouraged to make contact for further discussion and/or an informal visit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Rebecca Bradley&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Matron&lt;/p&gt;
